                    <span>This is a beautifully written book that captures the plight of pioneers traveling west.  My fourth grade students really gain a sense of what life was like once upon a time.  Great book!!...</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Lingering</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
