                    <span>when you start to read this story . it transforms you into a person in the donner party . this story really makes you take a second look on the donner party .</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">This book was great!!!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
